newsArray.title: PSL 10 anthem ‘X Dekho’ to be released tomorrow
creator: A Sports
newsArray.description: LAHORE: The Pakistan Cricket Board (PCB), on Tuesday, officially announced that the much-anticipated anthem for the Pakistan Super League (PSL) season 10, titled ‘X Dekho’, will be released on April 2. According to the details, the anthem is set to premiere at 5 PM (Pakistan Standard Time) on the official PSL YouTube channel. Bringing together [...]The post PSL 10 anthem ‘X Dekho’ to be released tomorrow appeared first on ASports.tv.
